Some celebrities aren't on good terms with all of their family members. Some family arguments can get intense and last a long time. Many celebrities prefer to keep their family relationships private, and don't speak publicly about them very often. Related: The Truth About Isabella Jane Cruise And Nicole Kidman's Relationship When her daughter Isabella got married in 2015 she didn't invite her mother, Nicole Kidman, nor her father Tom Cruise to her wedding.

item.description: Super dad! Tom Welling is expecting his second child with his pregnant wife, Jessica Rose Lee. The Smallville alum, 43, tried to sidestep comments about his upcoming arrival on the Tuesday, January 12, “Inside of You” podcast episode when host Michael Rosenbaum said the actor had “another kid on the way.” The New York native asked, “What? He received his PGA Tour card for 2009 after finishing 25th on the 2008 Nationwide Tour money list.

item.title: Drew Barrymore Pantsed by Daughter When She Doesn't Wear Underwear
item.description: Drew Barrymore is all about the no-underwear life, and her daughters have taken notice. “My daughter tries to pants me all the time too because she knows I’m not wearing any underwear,” Barrymore, 48, said during the Thursday, February 29, episode of her eponymous talk show. “It’s a joke. But yeah, I’m like, ‘Just make sure this is an inside-the-house thing.’” Barrymore shares two daughters, Olive and Frankie, with ex-husband Will Kopelman, and the girls have witnessed their mom’s flair for skipping undergarments.

item.title: Tessa Brooks Biography, Age, Wiki, Height, Weight, Boyfriend, Family & More
item.description: One of the best dancers on the Internet Today, Tessa Brooks is an American Dancer, Actress, and YouTuber who belongs to Fresno, California. She has a huge number of subscribers on her self-titled YouTube channel where she uploads some of her silky moves. The Gorgeous Lady is a well-known member of a dance crew, immaBeast, and also performed with The Pulse on Tour.  She was affiliated with a social group, Team 10 where she used to do work with artists like Jake Paul, Erika Costell, and many more.

item.title: Travis Kelce Shares How He Stays Grounded Amid Rumors Of Jealousy Issues With Taylor Swift
item.description: Highlights Travis Kelce insists he's grounded despite rumors of jealousy towards Taylor Swift's male dancers, emphasizing authenticity in personal life. Kelce shifts focus from personal life to upcoming acting role, highlighting his multifaceted career interests beyond NFL. Taylor Swift reportedly sets rules for Kelce in their relationship, including restrictions on interactions with other women to avoid media speculation. While he didn’t directly address accusations that he’s jealous, Travis Kelce insisted he’s a grounded guy when being grilled about his relationship with Taylor Swift .

item.title: Charlotte Flair Tells The Story Behind Her Figure Eight Finisher (Video)
item.description: Charlotte Flair happened to invent her Figure Eight finisher just by playing around in the ring.  According to a recent video on Fox’s WWE YouTube Channel, Charlotte tells the tale that NXT coach Sarah Amato simply suggested that she tried out a bridge while locking on her father’s classic hold and it ended up looking pretty great, so much that Simon Gotch suggested the “Figure Eight” name because it looked twice as good.

item.title: Houston Texans Sign Zach Cunningham To $58 Million Contract Extension

item.title: Why Are 'The Ultimatum' Cast Members So Young?
item.description: Netflix's new experimental dating show, The Ultimatum has been making waves worldwide. It's just crazy re-pairing couples with other couples to see if they still want to marry their original partners or move on. Having Love Is Blind hosts, Nick and Vanessa Lachey in the show — who've also had the same pre-marriage ultimatum — certainly gives the cast a "happy ending" to look forward to. Despite being hooked on the show, many fans think it's still crazy that these 20-somethings are already worried about such a huge commitment.

item.title: Will Ferrell, Jason Momoa to Costar as TV Father, Son in New Movie
item.description: Will Ferrell is set to play Jason Momoa‘s TV father in a new comedy film, and no one is more excited than the Game of Thrones star himself! Momoa, 37, shared a story about the news on Instagram on Friday, May 5, writing, “When u wake up Read this throw on some ice cube and start blasting ‘It was a good day’. running around the house like home alone Living the f–king dream WILL FERRELL is a god to me.

item.title: Joe Jonas, Sophie Turner's Daughter Loves Being a Big Sister'
item.description: Girl squad! Joe Jonas and Sophie Turner’s oldest daughter, Willa, has fully embraced her sibling, a source exclusively tells Us Weekly. “Willa loves being a big sister and having a sibling to play with,” the insider says of the 2-year-old. The Jonas Brothers singer, 33, and the Game of Thrones alum, 26, welcomed baby No. 2 in July. They have since kept their family life under wraps, including their newborn’s moniker.

item.title: Mandy Moore Steps Out Without Wedding Ring After Divorce News: Photos
item.description: Onward and upward! Mandy Moore has taken the next step with her divorce from estranged husband Ryan Adams — she’s ditched her wedding ring. The former teen pop star, who announced she’s calling it quits on her nearly six-year marriage to the musician last month, stepped out in L.A.’s Los Feliz nabe, on Monday, Feb. 16, without her sparkler while running errands. Wearing jeans and a simple white T-shirt, the Red Band Society actress, 30, looked refreshed after spending Valentine’s Day weekend on a retreat with BFF Minka Kelly.

item.title: Who Is Megan Weaver From Langham Creek High School? Is She Arrested?
item.description: Megan Weaver, a Langham Creek High School English educator capture news, has been the subject of broad tales. Is this data exact? To figure out additional, continue to peruse. Police have charged a previous Langham Creek High School English educator of physically connecting with one of her male understudies, as per examiners. Per the court papers, the Cypress-Fairbanks Independent School District Police Department started an examination after the gatekeepers of a 15-year-old kid informed the school about upsetting material and messages gained on the adolescent’s telephone.

item.title: Whoopi Goldberg and Sara Haines Recreate Ghost Pottery Scene
item.description: Whoopi Goldberg and Sara Haines are breathing new life into the iconic pottery scene from the 1990 film Ghost. The cohosts recreated the steamy movie moment during the Wednesday, December 13, episode of The View. During a holiday gift segment, Goldberg, 68, and Haines, 46, approached a table holding a motorized pottery wheel, prompting Goldberg to break out into a rendition of the Righteous Brothers’ “Unchained Melody,” which plays during the Ghost sequence that proved how sensual pottery making can be, especially when stars Demi Moore and Patrick Swayze are involved.

item.title: WWE Royal Rumble: Bianca Belair vs. Alexa Bliss Result
item.description: made short work of Alexa Bliss to retain her title tonight, and after the match, Bliss once again got a visit from a familiar face. In the WWE RAW Women’s Championship match, Belair put away Bliss quick after a slightly back-and-forth beginning.  In the end, Bianca blocked a dropkick attempt and hit Bliss with a DDT, before quickly hitting the KOD after a pinfall attempt that ended things and won her yet another title defense.

item.title: Alaina Marie Mathers Biography; Net Worth, Parents, Brother, High School And Songs Of Eminems Dau
item.description: Alaina Marie Mathers is the adopted child of Eminem. She was born on May 3, 1993, to Dawn Scott who is Eminem’s sister. Dawn became a drug addict and despite Eminem’s effort to get her out of addiction, she couldn’t get out of addiction hence, he adopted Alaina to provide her with a better upbringing. Alaina attended Cherokee Elementary school and then proceeded to Seneca Middle School and later graduated from the University of Oakland.

item.title: Becky Lynch Takes More Shots at Ronda Rousey on Twitter
item.description: The feud between Becky Lynch and Ronda Rousey has gone from a small rivalry to a full-blown hatred for each other, and with their triple threat match at WrestleMania 35 only days away, Lynch has taken to Twitter to once again take shots at Rousey. In a tweet shared earlier today, Lynch referenced Rousey’s remarks about her mother never teaching her to lose by saying that she would do what her mother didn’t.

item.title: Christophe Normand Net Worth
item.description: Christophe Normand (born October 17, 1991) is a professional Canadian football fullback for the Montreal Alouettes of the Canadian Football League (CFL). Normand played CIS football for the Laval Rouge et Or and was part of the 2012 and 2013 Vanier Cup championship teams. Christophe Normand’s net worth Aside from being the most well-liked Canadian football player, Christophe Normand is also one of the wealthiest. The sources we looked at—Wikipedia, Forbes, and Business Insider—estimated Christophe Normand’s net worth at $1.

item.description: Blake Lynch is an American football linebacker for the Minnesota Vikings of the National Football League. Blake Lynch was born on February 14, 1997, in Gilmer, Texas. Blake Lynch attended Gilmer High School. After redshirting in his freshman year, Blake Lynch played college football for Baylor, where he made 32 career starts at five different positions, including; cornerback, linebacker, safety, wide receiver and running back. In a four-year college career, Blake Lynch accrued 673 receiving yards, four receiving touchdowns and 79 rushing yards.
